Retrieve a single interface instance by UUID with decrypted fields.

Request body:
    {
        "instance_uuid": "uuid"
    }

Returns:
    {
        "instance": {...}  # Single instance object
    }

Update an interface instance with encrypted fields.

Request body:
    {
        "instance_uuid": "uuid",
        "instance_details": {
            "metadata": {...},          # Update custom metadata
            "answers": {...},           # Update latest form data
            "linked_entities": [{"entity_type": "workflow", "entity_uuid": "..."}],  # Update entity refs
            "last_activity_at": "now"   # Refresh activity timestamp
        }
    }

Returns:
    {
        "instance": {...}  # Updated instance
    }

Note:
    - Cannot update link_token_hash (security)
    - CAN update sent_to (to add/remove recipients - any email in array can authenticate)
    - Cannot update created_by (audit trail)
    - Use update-interface-instance-status to change status

Get the most recent answer for an instance.

Request body:
    {
        "instance_uuid": "uuid",
        "kind": "autosave"  # Optional: 'save', 'autosave', or 'submit'
    }

Returns:
    {
        "ok": true,
        "answer": {
            "answer_uuid": "uuid",
            "instance_uuid": "uuid",
            "kind": "autosave",
            "payload": {...},      # Form data
            "metadata": {...},     # User agent, IP hash, etc.
            "ts": "timestamp"
        }
    }

Returns 404 if no answers exist for this instance.

Get answer history for an instance (newest first).

Request body:
    {
        "instance_uuid": "uuid",
        "limit": 100,           # Optional: 1-1000, default 100
        "kind": "autosave"      # Optional: filter by type
