        "client_uuid": "uuid",           // Optional: filter by client
        "status": "OPEN"                 // Optional: filter by status
    }

If no filters provided, returns all threads.
Filters can be combined (AND logic).

Returns:
    {
        "threads": [...]  // List with parsed JSONB fields, ordered by created_at DESC
    }

Retrieve a single email thread by UUID.

Request body:
    {
        "thread_uuid": "uuid"
    }

Returns:
    {
        "thread": {...}
    }

Retrieve multiple email threads by UUIDs.

